## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all cultural perspectives on intelligence. The research is limited by the scope of the sources accessed, which primarily focus on Western and some non-Western cultures. Additionally, the dynamic nature of cultural evolution means that perceptions of intelligence may change over time, necessitating ongoing research in this field.

